    <p>Sidebar is JavaScript modal plugin to add dialogs to your site for lightboxes, user notifications, or completely custom content.</p>
</header>

<figure>
    <figcaption>How it works</figcaption>
    <p>
        Toggle a working sidebar demo by clicking the button below. It will slide down and fade in from the top of the page.
        Use <code>.toggle-show</code> class and <code>data-show="elementName"</code> data attribute to call the sidebar. For multiple sidebars be sure thet each one have different ID - elementName.
    </p>

